data.description: Come and view this Beautiful open floor plan home on one of the largest lots in all Spencer Creek Woods!! Most of the lots in the community are 6,000 - 7,000 SF. This home is sitting on 14,708 SF (.33 of an acre. This Beautiful home has Granite Countertops in the kitchen and 42' Maple cabinets, Hardwood flooring from the Foyer that flows into the Family room.  Ceramic tile in the kitchen and bathrooms. The kitchen has a Breakfast Bar and Formal dining area. This home features a Full Front porch and Full Rear porch. This home has a optional 4th bedroom (also known as the FROG). This home has several archways throughout the home. This home is a must see. It won't last long!!
